HEADWORD: Alfalfa
<hw>Al*fal"fa</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>The lucern (<spn>Medicago sativa</spn>), a
